      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable ride! It's in fair condition, showing some honest character and wear from its adventures, but it still has plenty of life left in it. This is a fantastic, budget-friendly choice for anyone looking for a reliable vehicle that gets you where you need to go without breaking the bank. A solid, functional car at a great price!",
