    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor road wear, including small stone chips on the hood and front fascia. The interior is clean and comfortable; while there is some light creasing on the driver's seat bolster, the upholstery remains free of rips or stains. All power features, including the climate control and infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car drives well with no known issues, offering a reliable and pleasant experience for the next owner.",
