    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey guys! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really nice condition and has plenty of life left for its next adventure! It handles super smoothly and is ready to hit the road today\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
